      "text": [
        " وُجُوهِهِمْ مِنْ أَثَرِ اَلسُّجُودِ» قَالَ «هُوَ اَلسَّهَرُ فِي اَلصَّلاَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1366 - Abdullah ibn Sinan asked him (Abu Abdullah (as)) about the words of Allah (swt), the Mighty and Majestic:\n\"Their mark is on their faces from the trace of prostration\" (Surah Al-Fath 48:29).\nImam (as) said: \"It refers to staying awake for prayer.\""
        ]
      }
